{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"title","type":"text","x":0,"y":-130,"width":2430,"height":80,"text":"# 🦛 Hippo — Dev Progress\nRoadmap (top) · Kanban (below) — snapshot: July 18, 2026. Full detail: [[00 Build Plan Overview]] · [[Open Decisions]] · [[Home]]"},
		{"id":"g0","type":"group","x":0,"y":0,"width":380,"height":360,"label":"Phase 0 — Foundations","color":"4"},
		{"id":"c0","type":"text","x":15,"y":45,"width":350,"height":300,"text":"**Weeks 1–2 · ✅ done**\n\n- Card protocol v1 (Zod, additive-only + fallback)\n- Eval harness v1 (300 queries, launch gates)\n- CI: build/test/size-gate/lint per PR"},
		{"id":"g1","type":"group","x":410,"y":0,"width":380,"height":360,"label":"Phase 1 — Thin Client SDK","color":"4"},
		{"id":"c1","type":"text","x":425,"y":45,"width":350,"height":300,"text":"**Weeks 2–6 · ✅ done (Jul 16)**\n\n- Core renderer, onboarding, share/feedback, mock-gateway demo\n- Posture matrix + tokenized themes (#12) · i18n + RTL (#15)\n- **Fold release** (`629251b`): contextual chips, composer v2 + drafts, scroll anchoring, offline outbox, a11y, settings (language + clear memory), brief copy — 108 tests\n- Remaining: Arabic copy (layout works, strings pending)"},
		{"id":"g2","type":"group","x":820,"y":0,"width":380,"height":360,"label":"Phase 2 — Intelligence Backend","color":"3"},
		{"id":"c2","type":"text","x":835,"y":45,"width":350,"height":300,"text":"**Weeks 4–10 · 🚧 nearly done**\n\n- Intelligence service merged (#8): intent + research, answer cache, guardrail, SSE streaming\n- Gateway core merged (#7) + streaming briefs (#9)\n- Memory v1 merged (#10) · Redis stores + OTel (#13)\n- Full loop verified live on qwen3:4b + market data\n- Open: the bake-off run vs 70B baseline (needs GPU)"},
		{"id":"g3","type":"group","x":1230,"y":0,"width":380,"height":360,"label":"Phase 3 — Execution Seam","color":"3"},
		{"id":"c3","type":"text","x":1245,"y":45,"width":350,"height":300,"text":"**Weeks 8–12 · 🚧 in progress**\n\n- Seam service + sim venue extracted from orchestrator\n- **Hand-built KoinBX adapter** (HMAC private trade API) + poll reconciler + audit log\n- Approach A locked (Open Decision #1)\n- Open: pilot-sandbox lifecycle round-trip · confirm-surface mode (Decision #6)"},
		{"id":"g4","type":"group","x":1640,"y":0,"width":380,"height":360,"label":"Phase 4 — Agentic Installer","color":"3"},
		{"id":"c4","type":"text","x":1655,"y":45,"width":350,"height":300,"text":"**Weeks 10–14 · 🚧 in progress**\n\n- `hippo scan v0` (discovery → integration report)\n- CTI conformance suite + `hippo conform`\n- Stage 3: deterministic adapter.config.yaml generator\n- Stage 4: mapping.ts + rejections.yaml codegen\n- Open: embed injection · second-venue dogfood"},
		{"id":"g5","type":"group","x":2050,"y":0,"width":380,"height":360,"label":"Phase 5 — Pilot Launch","color":"6"},
		{"id":"c5","type":"text","x":2065,"y":45,"width":350,"height":300,"text":"**Weeks 12–16 · ⬜ not started**\n\n- Onboarding hero live, ambient pulse, share cards (client parts shipped in Phase 1)\n- Pilot instrumentation: cache hit rate, queries/MAU, cost/MAU, lift telemetry\n- Degraded-mode banner demonstrable for procurement"},
